description:
When a gifted ghostwriter (Ewan McGregor) is hired to write the memoirs of former British Prime Minister Adam Lang (Pierce Brosnan), he quickly finds himself trapped in a web of political and sexual intrigue.

Lang is implicated in a scandal over his administration\'s harsh tactics, and as the ghostwriter digs into the politician\'s past, he discovers secrets that threaten to jeopardize international relations forever...

